data.description: Discover a beautifully and elegantly updated residence in Simpsonville's desirable Hunters Woods neighborhood. This home seamlessly blends modern comfort with classic charm, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere.  Upon entering, the home welcomes you with brand-new bamboo flooring throughout and a thoughtfully reconfigured floor plan. Notable interior features include an expanded laundry room for added convenience.   The kitchen, a true focal point, has undergone a stunning transformation. It showcases an elegant design, making it perfect for everyday cooking and entertaining. All appliances are included in the sale, streamlining your move-in process.  Custom-built storage solutions and shiplap accents are incorporated throughout the home, enhancing its character and functionality.  Situated on a corner lot, inside a peaceful cul-de-sac, the property boasts a beautifully landscaped yard. The backyard offers a serene retreat, ideal for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing and grilling. You'll also appreciate the screened-in back porch for unwinding or catching your favorite sports events.  Additional highlights include updated plumbing and electrical systems, ensuring both safety and modern convenience. The entire property has been re-landscaped, creating a welcoming and well-maintained exterior.  Don't miss the chance to make this your new home. Schedule a personal showing to fully appreciate all that this gorgeous property has to offer. This is an exceptional opportunity to live in a beautifully updated home in the coveted Hunters Woods neighborhood.   *Home has been completely updated with new bamboo flooring, paint, floor plan adjustments and added square footage.  All plumbing and most electrical were completely replaced.  New Granite counter tops, new water heater, upper level HVAC was replaced, new tile flooring, new toilets, two new back decks, raised garden and plenty of additional landscaping including new rock patio and rock retention.*
